{"tid":973110,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真Post］同女仔第一次Dating帶佢食乜好？","createTime":"2019-01-08T01:25:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T02:25:28.000Z","uid":213807,"like":33,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"93f8ca3cab41696c37f065577b1a1b29fc159e4b","tid":973110,"uid":213807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T01:25:03.000Z","msg":"小弟今年係聖誕Party到識左個女仔，佢都幾開朗健談。呢幾日同佢傾開食野同餐廳既話題，咁我諗住約佢出黎食飯。<br />\n<br />\n但係我自己平時食開譚仔、大家樂之類既連鎖餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。本身對食又無咩要求。唔想第一次約會就帶佢去食D咁頹既野。好想可以比個好D既第一印象佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個女仔唔夠一米六高，細細粒應該唔大食。求巴絲介紹D精緻少少或者特別D既餐廳比小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。 最好係九龍區。"},{"pid":"ced4ccb339b08afa982404f81e02aec1b3511470","tid":973110,"uid":76519,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T01:27:35.000Z","msg":"咁你有冇問過佢鍾意食咩？"},{"pid":"8ba00b40daefbfae10b356aec47a903dc8d189e9","tid":973110,"uid":18932,"like":137,"dislike":0,"score":137,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T01:27:48.000Z","msg":"Cafe de corel"},{"pid":"53158a0cc940418c026595903c1348cf79775344","tid":973110,"uid":107364,"like":7,"dislike":60,"score":-53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T01:28:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3234e7e78aff79af84b91f426957bfad3aabbc51","tid":973110,"uid":213807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ced4ccb339b08afa982404f81e02aec1b3511470","tid":973110,"uid":76519,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T01:27:35.000Z","msg":"咁你有冇問過佢鍾意食咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T01:29:10.000Z","msg":"有呀。但佢既答案好似無所謂。我淨係知佢唔食辣囉。"},{"pid":"bd67f5bf83e2516a79e4d6ad37edeba134f451ff","tid":973110,"uid":58685,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T01:29:24.000Z","msg":"梗係問佢想食咩好啦"},{"pid":"20a424ae95c5f911a13202d8aea7ec1e4b7e877a","tid":973110,"uid":2